Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.promo.pcfg.Parser

  • public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides the top-level API and command-line interface to train and test the Stanford Parser on a completely unlabeled training document via an initial seed model.

    Heath Vinicombe
